\begin_layout Section
Hypotheses
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Simultaneous sensor and actuator distribution can be achieved and is more
 efficient i.e.
 these are not independent problems, and these can be formulated as a ILP
 and solved.
\end_layout

